{"tid":414554,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"中學出來做野vs讀完大學搵野做","createTime":"2017-09-26T10:18:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T04:05:37.000Z","uid":137997,"like":63,"dislike":51,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2cf559e3faba1ec2ef3902c071fd666a7be1976a","tid":414554,"uid":137997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T10:18:13.000Z","msg":"邊樣抵 有無邊位巴絲分享下經驗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 中學出來做野早做早有經驗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 讀好啲書為未來鋪路<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我仲讀緊ive 雖然未必夠料讀大學 但係諗起人地唔讀書出來做野 到我第時讀完出來做野撞到佢地就熟手老屎忽 自己先新手上路就唔知點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aabb1d6599540353d5c950f868756664d180fc3a","tid":414554,"uid":140296,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T10:23:04.000Z","msg":"點解唔一路讀書一路返part time?"},{"pid":"5ece1987edec36930c6da130b7782f66df3b02d8","tid":414554,"uid":103759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T10:24:40.000Z","msg":"睇你做咩啦 <br />\nSell屎肯定冇分別"},{"pid":"90faf98f350569ad4f214af3ba1bf798f333449e","tid":414554,"uid":92921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T10:29:59.000Z","msg":"睇你讀咩啦，有啲工要讀番來"},{"pid":"84575d806b36801a7a4d18b07a00251c2cfdf90c","tid":414554,"uid":137997,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T10:33:59.000Z","msg":"再想問多樣野 你地返part time通常咩時候返<br />\n<br />\n 朝早返學 放學就返 定禮拜六日返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之前有返過惠康"},{"pid":"100c05406d451552fe92520895bad963e28c5250","tid":414554,"uid":29608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T10:35:40.000Z","msg":"有好多工無大學學歷唔會請。<br />\n<br />\n同埋工作經驗係要相關先叫工作經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5306beed39ea72a34b68fbf51b5bc8de69ce44a","tid":414554,"uid":143783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0